caller_intent: The caller (Jane Johnson) wants to shop for a cheaper homeowner's insurance rate for a policy under Brian Rominger, addressing a recent rate increase.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the policyholder's name (Brian Rominger) after initial spelling error.
Asked about roof age (1 year old, replaced last year), pets (Chihuahua mix), and property features (no pools/trampolines or security systems).
Verified contact information and confirmed Progressive is the current auto insurer.
Noted Brian has two Progressive policies (commercial and personal vehicle) for potential package discounts.
Agreed to run quotes through multiple carriers and contact the caller with results.
knowledge_required: Insurance rate factors (roof age, pet types, discounts)
summary: Jane Johnson requested a homeowner's insurance rate review for Brian Rominger's policy, citing a rate increase. The agent gathered details about property features, pets, and auto insurance (Progressive) to compare carrier options. A callback will follow with potential cheaper rates and discount opportunities.
